CustomField.formula: IF(ISBLANK(TEXT(Asset_Latitude_Longitude__Latitude__s)) || ISBLANK(TEXT(Asset_Latitude_Longitude__Longitude__s)), "No location available", HYPERLINK ("https://www.google.com/maps?q=" & TEXT(Asset_Latitude_Longitude__Latitude__s) & "," & TEXT(Asset_Latitude_Longitude__Longitude__s), "View Asset Address on Google Maps"))
CustomField.label: Asset Map
